Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:59.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Why should I go to New York for a mechanical pencil...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:12.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,535.714)}{\fs47.143}{\3c&HAA0000&}Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:12.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,600)}{\fs47.143}{\3c&HAA0000&}Suga Kenji
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:12.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There! Popular producer figure, Suga! By the order from Matsumoto, he'll now act as the saboteur!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.30,suga,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:18.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Is he on vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:19.90,suga,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.30,suga,,0,0,0,,I'm going to visit New York for a week, then I go to Bahamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.90,suga,,0,0,0,,Well, What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,Don't "What are you doing here" me! I'm on Batsu Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.10,suga,,0,0,0,,Ah, I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:29.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,You know it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.62,hamada,,0,0,0,,We'll go togethe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:32.90,suga,,0,0,0,,There's no way around. I'll lead you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:33.62,hamada,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,This whole thing is lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:41.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that, the trip for New york has finally begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:46.70,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(84.094,584)}{\pos(156.094,600)}Plane that Hamada is on board now left for New York...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,600)}Of course, Economy class for Batsu Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Shimizu, where's Suga, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,I think he's at at the front seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.10,hamada,,0,0,0,,Front seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,What do you mean front?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.50,generic2,,0,0,0,,Front all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:05.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,So he makes actors sit on economy class but not himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.62,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,600)}Producer Sugawara is relaxing in business class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:28.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm on economy class, goddamit! Why are you in business class?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:34.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Hey, He's drinking cognac! Disgusting fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With all these swing, he couldn't sleep at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:40.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}15 hours after departure, they have arrived at JFK International Airport!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:40.10,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(126.85,25.143)}{\pos(101.25,17.143)\c&H0000FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&}15 hours {\1c&HFF1111&}since departure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:40.10,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,570)}{\4c&H0000AA&}{\shad5}JFK International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:05:01.82,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fs35}{\pos(105.469,548.571)}{\1c&HDD5533&}GnT Special Program
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:05:01.82,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fs35}{\pos(105.469,600)}{\1c&H3333BB&}Hama-chan Batsu Game
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:45.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For just one machine pencil, Hamada Masatoshi has landed on America!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.50,hamada,,0,0,0,,We're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:54.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,It's literally the worst... I'm so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.70,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hamada is now en route for Sakamoto's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:03.50,hamada,,0,0,0,,Argh, why the white team lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.50,suga,,0,0,0,,Are you reading the trend of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.82,hamada,,0,0,0,,Shit, Amagasaki has developed a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.82,generic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs35}Note: Amagasaki is the hometown for Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:13.30,suga,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't...
