Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:18.50,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They arrives at the center of world's economics and culture, Manhattan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heading for Mr.Sakamoto's apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:29.10,hamada,,0,0,0,,No, we're going to Kyoju's house! Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:31.30,generic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs30}Note: Ryuichi Sakamoto is called as "Kyoju", which means professor, named by his friend and musician Yukihiro Takahasi for he knew lots of knowledge and theory about music.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:38.02,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\pos(194.063,545)}Suga's sabotage scheme has started!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:34.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:36.50,hamada,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:38.50,hamada,,0,0,0,,Kyoju's place's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.30,suga,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,Wait, where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.50,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,570)}{\4c&H0000AA&}{\shad5}Empire State Building
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.50,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the symbol of Manhattan, Empire State Building!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:50.70,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An unwanted stop for Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,It's so cold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,So cold, wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.10,hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh shit It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.62,hamada,,0,0,0,,But the view from here is good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,It's impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:04.90,suga,,0,0,0,,Let's take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:05.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.02,hamada,,0,0,0,,Picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:10.50,hamada,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.10,hamada,,0,0,0,,Why the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.90,suga,,0,0,0,,Why not? It's famous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.90,suga,,0,0,0,,That's it, good, good, it's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:18.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,No, it's hella lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:28.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\pos(105.469,480)}Popular in Empire State Building
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:28.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\pos(105.469,545)}By punching a one cent coin, it can make pendant with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:28.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\pos(105.469,608.571)}the design of building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:26.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Moreover, Hamada is forced to buy unwanted coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this!? It's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.70,suga,,0,0,0,,Ok, next we'll go skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,Don't be an idiot.
