Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:41.10,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another famous spot in New York, the skating rink in Rockefeller Center!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh watch out, watch out...
