Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:59.10,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,570)}{\4c&H0000AA&}{\shad5}Times Square
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.10,generic2,,0,0,0,,Next, for the center, Times Square!
