Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:07.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,Nevermind about the hot dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.50,suga,,0,0,0,,"Nevermind about the hot dog..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.70,suga,,0,0,0,,Why don't we get one since we're already here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:15.90,suga,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:22.70,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hamada has no time for a hot dog. He's irritated, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.50,suga,,0,0,0,,Hama-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.50,hamada,,0,0,0,,You don't have to take a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.50,suga,,0,0,0,,Eat it, eat it now...
