Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:44.50,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}21 hours after they departed from Tokyo, they finally reached the apartment where Sakamoto Ryuichi lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's livin' in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,Or is this his office?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.70,suga,,0,0,0,,I guess he's living in here, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,Don't "I don't know" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:53.50,suga,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:58.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, reunification with Sakamoto Ryuichi after a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.62,hamada,,0,0,0,,I hope he's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.10,hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kyoju!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:10.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,Hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:14.50,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,591.429)}{\fs47.143}{\3c&HAA0000&}Sakamoto Ryuichi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:15.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm here because...Matsumoto's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.10,hamada,,0,0,0,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.10,hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm here to fetch something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:21.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,Um, Matsumoto's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,I've come all the way from Tokyo, what's with that attitude!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:39.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through Kyoju's hand, the machine pencil is warmly handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Batsu Game completes splendidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:42.30,generic,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\move(1080,570,105.469,570,100,2700)}{\1c&H0033BB&}{\fs51.429}{\fnVerdana}Mechanical Pencil fetching success!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.50,hamada,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, Sakamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:48.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,Ryuichi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:49.90,suga,,0,0,0,,Let's just go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,No, no way that attitude is allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.10,hamada,,0,0,0,,I can't go back like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,Let me have a talk with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:01.70,suga,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you're so popular and exalted in Japan, but this is how it is here, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:07.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,It's fucking frustrating...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,Cold, cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.10,suga,,0,0,0,,Go to airport now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:13.10,hamada,,0,0,0,,Who? Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,You're not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:17.70,suga,,0,0,0,,Well, no. I'm here for vacation. I told you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:21.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, right. Then, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.70,hamada,,0,0,0,,Ugh, this is the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.30,suga,,0,0,0,,Bye, Hama-chan...
