Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.34,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.94,hosei,,0,0,0,,Is that it? Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.54,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's even got my name "Matsumoto" written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.74,hamada,,0,0,0,,Suga kept getting in my way and slowing me down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.74,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, this is over now, it doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.14,hamada,,0,0,0,,It was so cold too...
