Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.18,hosei,,0,0,0,,Really? What's up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:11:00.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, calm down, what eraser are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:04.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter anymore since I already fetched this for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:06.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:07.98,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna call Mr. Sakamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:08.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,Who cares about this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:13.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,I already went there and did the Batsu Game, it was so tiring and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:14.58,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Um, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:15.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.18,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:16.98,generic2,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:17.98,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is this Kyoju?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.98,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:38.58,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fs47.143}{\pos(506.25,548.571)}On the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:38.58,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fs47.143}{\pos(506.25,612.857)}Sakamoto Ryuichi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:20.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.78,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is Matsumoto speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice to hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:23.78,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Same here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:24.78,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I have just noticed this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.38,generic2,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.58,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find the eraser that was with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.98,generic2,,0,0,0,,Um, it was left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:33.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,Where was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.18,generic2,,0,0,0,,Here, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:39.18,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,D-Did you just find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.98,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go fetch it?
