Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:03.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manhattan, New York. A long time no see city welcomes Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:09.58,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(163.25,25.143)}{\pos(101.25,17.143)}{\c&H0000FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&}56 hours {\1c&HFF1111&}since the first departure
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:11.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,W-Wait...Stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Is that Suga-chan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,I hate this kind of setup...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Stop setting up these coincidental meet-ups already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Ugh, here I am again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:34.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,I just want to go to Kyoju's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:38.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:41.78,suga,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,Don't be saying "What?" to me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,Ugh...I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:46.98,suga,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,When I went home, he asked me to come back and fetch his eraser this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.78,suga,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,I have to go to Kyoju's place again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:53.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's go together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:55.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,Don't make me take detours again this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:57.58,suga,,0,0,0,,Look, I ha-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:58.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,And I se-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell is your outfit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's just go! Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm already so mad now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:07.70,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A reunion with Producer Suga after a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.18,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another Times Square after two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.70,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,575)}{\4c&H0000AA&}{\shad5}Times Square
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.38,suga,,0,0,0,,Why are you here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Don't be asking me that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:17.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,Like I told you earlier, I'm here to fetch the eraser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.78,suga,,0,0,0,,Let's eat hot dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,Y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:24.98,suga,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:26.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Haven't we been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:27.78,suga,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,It's the same place and the same guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:32.18,suga,,0,0,0,,It's always good to visit New York again after a long time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:33.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,I ain't visiting here "after a long time"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:39.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,It's ok, but let's just hurry up on the eraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.18,suga,,0,0,0,,Ah, that won't be any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.78,suga,,0,0,0,,Have you done any shopping here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:44.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,Shopping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:48.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Of course not! I'm on a mission here! I didn't even get any souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:52.18,suga,,0,0,0,,No problem! Let's just go shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,Why the hell should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:57.18,suga,,0,0,0,,C'mon, why not! Let's just go shopping for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.38,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,575)}{\4c&H0000AA&}{\shad5}5th Avenue
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:03.18,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}New York's 5th Avenue! So many world class boutiques are located here! Truly the Mecca of shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:11.38,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And of course, Hamada is dragged around town once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:14.98,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,575)}{\4c&H0000AA&}{\shad5}East Village
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.58,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}East Village after two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:20.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(173.25,25.143)}{\pos(101.25,17.143)}{\c&H0000FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&}59 hours {\1c&HFF1111&}since the first departure
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.50,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is now has been 59 hours since the first departure from Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:23.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the Batsu Game is finally reaching its climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,How is this also part of the Batsu Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:26.78,suga,,0,0,0,,Since you lost that bet, can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,Why must I do this again? That's what's annoying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.38,suga,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,It's cold here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:40.58,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another reunion with Sakamoto Ryuichi after 38 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:52.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kyoju!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,The eraser?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.38,generic2,,0,0,0,,You're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:02.50,hamada,,0,0,0,,What do you mean we're late?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.50,hamada,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,Sakamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:06.90,generic2,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. Sorry. That's what I came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:17.30,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through Kyoju's hand, the eraser is warmly handed, describing parabola.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Batsu Game is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:18.58,generic,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\move(1080,561.429,156.094,561.429,100,2700)}{\1c&H0033BB&}{\fs51.429}{\fnVerdana}Eraser fetching success!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,It's so irritating...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.78,suga,,0,0,0,,Let's go, you already got the eraser...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,That's how Grammy Awards change a man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,Alright then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,I'll start making music tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:36.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna challenge you! I'm gonna make music...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,I'll meet you again at the next Grammy Award ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:40.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,Farewell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:45.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(57.219,507)}{\pos(139.219,515)}Eraser's fetched. Hamada is off from New York once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, to Japan where Matsumoto awaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.58,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,565.714)}{\4c&H0000AA&}{\shad5}Board room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.18,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.38,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:58.78,generic2,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(159.25,27.429)}{\pos(101.25,21.429)}{\c&H0000FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&}78 hours {\1c&HFF1111&}since the first departure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:15:59.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,Is this it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.78,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah! This is the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:05.18,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Y'know...you should've checked for this eraser the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.58,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Now it's finally complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.38,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, I want Evian water too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:13.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Here you go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.78,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No, not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:17.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.18,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.18,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Go draw some Evian water in France.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:29.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.10,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You should have gone to France.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,WHY!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.38,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Considering audience's reaction, it's so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh they are like "Oh he goes to France now?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:46.78,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:49.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,Still, going to New York was really exhausting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.70,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I've heard that was tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, VERY TIRING!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:53.98,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Moreover, you didn't have any sleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just had to go back in a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:59.58,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, you had to go through that because I experienced similar things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,What similar thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.38,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The next Batsu Game is already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.98,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.18,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You go to the North Pole...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:14.38,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...and become Coolmint gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:17.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,Penguin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.58,generic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Note: Reference from advertising from Coolmint gum, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.18,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna sell that from Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.78,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like some kind of limited products.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:26.90,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:31.90,hamada,,0,0,0,,When I was in the plane, there was a couple behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:36.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,Then, the girl said to me "Can I have your autograph?".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,I said it's ok. I have nothing to do after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:43.58,hamada,,0,0,0,,She said, "I'm gonna take my clothes off". I was like, "Huh!?".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:49.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,She hand me her bra and said, "Sign to this".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.58,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's totally insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,It was so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,I signed that warm bra...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.58,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Don't smell it man, don't smell it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:09.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,Also, I didn't eat anything on the plane home. Because I was too tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:10.78,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.30,hamada,,0,0,0,,I didn't give a shit about food in the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,When I was sleeping all the way, about 5 hours left,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:21.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,A foreigner cabin attendant who spoke Japanese very well came to me and said-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:25.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,"You didn't eat anything, right?". Then, I responded "Yeah.".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:30.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,"If you go back from foreign country and didn't eat anything-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,you'll be mistaken as a drug mule."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.18,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:41.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,She said drug mules often don't eat anything and just go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:45.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,If they eat anything, drugs will go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:49.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,So they wrap drugs into plastic bag or something and swallow it-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.18,hamada,,0,0,0,,then they bring it to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:55.38,hamada,,0,0,0,,Since I haven't eaten anything, and just kept sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:19:01.98,hamada,,0,0,0,,Other foreign attendants kept looking at me when they pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:06.78,hamada,,0,0,0,,She said "You are not a drug mule, aren't you?", I was like "Hell no!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.78,matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, but...you were carrying drugs...

